---
title: Glazed Turkey Meatballs with Loaded Potato Wedges and Side Salad
description: Get a load of this meal! BBQ sauce-slathered turkey meatballs and loaded potato wedges come together for a delightful explosion of flavours. Grab some napkins and dig in!
